552
00:36:44.324 --> 00:36:46.907
(Tawnie sighs)

553
00:36:48.900 --> 00:36:50.463
- Look. Joshua's gone. Ari.

554
00:36:52.604 --> 00:36:54.733
The sooner you can
accept that. the better.

555
00:36:55.600 --> 00:36:58.610
- If it were Gabriel.
you would feel different.

556
00:36:58.610 --> 00:37:02.460
- Look. sometimes when
there's an accident.

