00:48:57.275 --> 00:48:59.858
(folder slams)

692
00:49:01.020 --> 00:49:04.960
- Every time a child goes
missing in this town.

693
00:49:04.960 --> 00:49:06.393
you're somewhere nearby.

694
00:49:07.930 --> 00:49:09.273
That a coincidence. Frank?

