00:51:24.730 --> 00:51:25.573
- Then can I go?

739
00:51:30.297 --> 00:51:32.737
(Lenny sighs)

740
00:51:32.737 --> 00:51:33.570
- Yeah.

741
00:51:38.060 --> 00:51:39.839
(door squeaks)

742
00:51:39.839 --> 00:51:41.839
(sighs)

743
