00:52:13.990 --> 00:52:15.143
- Yes. sweetie.

752
00:52:16.170 --> 00:52:17.533
I miss Cody very much.

753
00:52:19.950 --> 00:52:22.133
- Mommy said not to ask you about him.

754
00:52:23.370 --> 00:52:25.513
